results.name: Number of reduced words of length n in the Weyl group A_8.
comment: Computed with MAGMA using commands similar to those used to compute A161409.
reference: J. E. Humphreys, Reflection Groups and Coxeter Groups, Cambridge, 1990. See under Poincaré polynomial.
N. Bourbaki, Groupes et alg. de Lie, Chap. 4, 5, 6. (The group is defined in Planche I.)
formula: G.f. for A_m is the polynomial Prod_{k=1..m}(1-x^(k+1))/(1-x). Only finitely many terms are nonzero. This is a row of the triangle in A008302.
results.author: _John Cannon_ and _N. J. A. Sloane_, Nov 30 2009
